{"_path":"/city/t018","_dir":"city","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"智慧停車增605格 行動支付享半價","description":null,"image":"/images/city/t018-1.jpeg","sequence":18,"category":"智慧城市","author":"交通局","link":"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/Taoyuan/paper/1638087","head":{"meta":[{"name":"keywords","content":""},{"name":"robots","content":""},{"name":"author","content":""},{"name":"copyright","content":"© 2024 A7新林口-社區網站"},{"name":"og:title","content":"地方行政"}]},"publishedAt":"2024-03-29T00:00:00.000Z","toc":true,"body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"智慧停車增-605-格-行動支付享半價"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"智慧停車增 605 格 行動支付享半價"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"自由時報 2024/03/29 "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/Taoyuan/paper/1638087"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"智慧停車"}]},{"type":"text","value":":\n林口長庚醫院旁 5 路段、桃園火車站周邊 17 要道智慧停車增 605 格 行動支付享半價, 4 月起優惠 1 年。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"第二階段建置區域，林口長庚醫院周邊的復興一路、文化二路、文化三路、公園路及復興街等五條停車密集路段，使用智慧停車柱，提供一七 ○ 席停車位。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"智慧停車柱以柱上的影像辨識系統，偵測車輛停放及車號，車輛停好就計費，離去時就能行動支付繳費；地磁設備只能偵測車輛停放，無法掃描車號，仍採人工開單，以地磁偵測到車輛的時間立單，民眾可於車輛駛離停車格的十五分鐘後，直接掃描地磁停車單的 QR Code 查詢費用並行動支付繳費。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"與市府合作的行動支付業者有「車麻吉」、「friDay 理財+」、「街口支付」、「歐付寶」、「Easy Wallet 悠遊付」、「全支付」、「停車大聲公」、「一卡通 MONEY」、「icash Pay」、「Pi 行動錢包」。 請參考 "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://epark.tycg.gov.tw/public/download/%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C%E8%AA%AA%E6%98%8E-%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95%E6%94%AF%E4%BB%98APP%E7%B9%B3%E5%81%9C%E8%BB%8A%E8%B2%BB.pdf"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"行動支付 繳停車費說明"}]},{"type":"text","value":"。 及安裝 桃園輕鬆 GO App "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=tw.gov.tycg.app.android.etransportat